data.description: Charming, updated and move in ready!  This adorable home is in a quiet neighborhood, located in the historic town of Clifton and only about 30 minutes into Waco.  The interior of the home is so beautiful, featuring fresh farmhouse detailing throughout.  The large dining room makes for a perfect space for entertaining guests.  An added bonus is the home comes with the washer, dryer, gas range and microwave.   The exterior of the home has been updated with a timeless, farmhouse blue and is just gorgeous.  The large backyard has plenty of space to enjoy the outdoors, is shaded with mature pecan trees and has storage shed for your extra items.  This home is truly amazing and calling your name!
